[Sanjie Police Station, Qingzhou Branch,
Lihai Public Security Bureau]

4
00:04:33,390 --> 00:04:34,440
Help!

5
00:04:50,720 --> 00:04:51,430
Let go.

6
00:04:52,750 --> 00:04:53,480
Let go.

7
00:04:54,030 --> 00:04:55,750
Let go!

8
00:04:56,040 --> 00:04:57,850
Let go!

9
00:04:58,040 --> 00:04:59,330
You killed Zishan.

10
00:04:59,510 --> 00:05:01,160
I won't let you go.

11
00:05:21,390 --> 00:05:21,920
Mom!

12
00:05:22,830 --> 00:05:23,360
Mom!

13
00:05:24,040 --> 00:05:24,740
Mom!

14
00:05:27,240 --> 00:05:28,050
Mom!

15
00:05:28,720 --> 00:05:29,520
Mom!

16
00:05:32,680 --> 00:05:33,630
Is anyone there?

17
00:05:33,630 --> 00:05:34,270
Mom!

18
00:05:34,270 --> 00:05:35,710
Is anyone over there?

19
00:05:36,560 --> 00:05:38,030
Is anyone over there?

20
00:05:39,360 --> 00:05:40,310
Is anyone there?

21
00:05:41,390 --> 00:05:42,380
Mom!

22
00:05:43,270 --> 00:05:44,960
Is anyone inside?

23
00:05:45,680 --> 00:05:46,960
Is anyone there?

24
00:05:47,070 --> 00:05:48,800
Mom!

25
00:05:49,360 --> 00:05:50,480
Where are you?

26
00:05:51,480 --> 00:05:52,720
-Is anyone there?
-Mom!

27
00:05:52,720 --> 00:05:54,020
Help!

28
00:05:57,360 --> 00:05:58,920
-Mom!
-Help!

29
00:05:59,270 --> 00:06:00,000
Mom!

30
00:06:00,270 --> 00:06:01,000
Mom!

31
00:06:02,000 --> 00:06:02,940
Mom!

32
00:06:04,190 --> 00:06:05,420
Mom!

33
00:06:05,560 --> 00:06:07,160
Mom!

34
00:06:09,200 --> 00:06:10,820
-Help!
-Mom!

35
00:06:11,000 --> 00:06:13,680
-Help!
-Mom!

36
00:07:27,510 --> 00:07:28,570
What are you doing?

37
00:07:33,980 --> 00:07:34,980
How did you get in?

38
00:08:00,050 --> 00:08:01,100
I knew it was you.

39
00:08:08,370 --> 00:08:08,990
Hello.

40
00:08:09,230 --> 00:08:10,830
Your idea is very inspiring.

41
00:08:11,100 --> 00:08:12,800
Instigating Qiao Zishan to kill her mother

42
00:08:12,800 --> 00:08:14,040
shouldn't be the reason that scared Mister

43
00:08:14,040 --> 00:08:15,540
and made him close the Amusement Park.

44
00:08:15,540 --> 00:08:16,000
Yes.

45
00:08:16,960 --> 00:08:18,560
If that were really the case,

46
00:08:18,740 --> 00:08:19,510
he should have proudly

47
00:08:19,510 --> 00:08:21,860
publicized it all over the Amusement Park.

48
00:08:21,860 --> 00:08:23,260
We analyzed this before.

49
00:08:23,630 --> 00:08:25,160
His sudden closure of the Amusement Park

50
00:08:25,160 --> 00:08:27,000
is likely due to some emergency

51
00:08:27,000 --> 00:08:28,730
that made him feel endangered.

52
00:08:28,870 --> 00:08:29,830
I asked a mainland forensic doctor

53
00:08:29,830 --> 00:08:32,620
to carefully review
Qiao Lihua's autopsy report.

54
00:08:32,620 --> 00:08:35,820
He was suspicious about the wound
on the deceased's head.

55
00:08:35,870 --> 00:08:37,789
He thinks it could be a crush injury,

56
00:08:37,789 --> 00:08:40,350
or a blow from a curved blunt object.

57
00:08:40,640 --> 00:08:44,480
Did he really kill someone himself?

58
00:08:45,000 --> 00:08:46,480
It's impossible to tell right now.

59
00:08:46,480 --> 00:08:48,440
If there are clues
about the murder weapon,

60
00:08:48,440 --> 00:08:49,840
it would be very helpful.

61
00:08:50,160 --> 00:08:51,400
Then... What is that?

62
00:08:52,080 --> 00:08:53,880
It should have a certain weight.

63
00:08:54,490 --> 00:08:57,870
It might have a curved shape.

64
00:08:58,200 --> 00:09:01,380
This is a gift Yuan gave to Xiao Su.

65
00:09:02,240 --> 00:09:03,600
He liked it the most

66
00:09:04,240 --> 00:09:05,970
and always carried it with him.

67
00:09:06,710 --> 00:09:08,770
[NO SMOKING]

68
00:09:08,160 --> 00:09:08,960
Officers,

69
00:09:08,770 --> 00:09:12,210
[Upstairs]

70
00:09:09,360 --> 00:09:11,490
a lady just asked me to give this to you.

71
00:09:24,850 --> 00:09:25,150
[July 22, 2019]

72
00:09:27,380 --> 00:09:28,710
[July 22, 2019]

73
00:09:35,390 --> 00:09:37,120
No biological

74
00:09:37,120 --> 00:09:38,200
DNA samples were detected on this.

75
00:09:37,780 --> 00:09:38,430
[Sample No. 1 submitted for examination
yielded no findings.]

76
00:09:38,450 --> 00:09:39,260
[STR classification: No DNA remains]

77
00:09:39,200 --> 00:09:40,060
Keep this safe.

78
00:09:59,750 --> 00:10:03,150
This is the only thing your sister
left you to remember her by.

79
00:10:04,600 --> 00:10:06,800
Actually, you don't have to destroy it.

80
00:10:07,550 --> 00:10:10,280
Officer Li and the others
have already tested it.

81
00:10:10,390 --> 00:10:12,510
There's no DNA residue on it.

82
00:10:22,550 --> 00:10:23,750
When did it start?

83
00:10:26,320 --> 00:10:27,600
When my mom met you?

84
00:10:30,550 --> 00:10:30,910
No,

85
00:10:32,390 --> 00:10:33,190
even earlier.

86
00:10:35,720 --> 00:10:37,440
When Officer Li called you,

87
00:10:38,960 --> 00:10:40,560
you completely betrayed me.

88
00:10:41,750 --> 00:10:42,720
Why me?

89
00:10:45,510 --> 00:10:46,570
Because I love you.

90
00:10:47,840 --> 00:10:48,240
Love?

91
00:10:52,910 --> 00:10:54,640
Just like how you loved He Xiao,

92
00:10:55,480 --> 00:10:56,440
Xie Ke,

93
00:10:57,670 --> 00:10:58,630
Wei Zhihua,

94
00:10:59,030 --> 00:11:00,150
and Qiao Zishan?

95
00:11:10,550 --> 00:11:12,080
How can they compare to you?

96
00:11:14,290 --> 00:11:15,400
You are my wife.

97
00:11:17,630 --> 00:11:20,490
We are going to spend
the rest of our lives together.

98
00:11:20,790 --> 00:11:21,480
Are we?

99
00:11:25,840 --> 00:11:28,440
You've probably said
these things to them too.

100
00:11:29,790 --> 00:11:31,240
He Xiao funded you

101
00:11:31,750 --> 00:11:34,150
to go to Harbor Island
for graduate school.

102
00:11:34,510 --> 00:11:36,370
She abandoned her family for you.

103
00:11:38,600 --> 00:11:40,120
I've told you this before.

104
00:11:42,200 --> 00:11:43,800
It was her wishful thinking.

105
00:11:46,630 --> 00:11:47,360
Was it?

106
00:11:48,440 --> 00:11:49,790
Wasn't it because you

107
00:11:50,360 --> 00:11:51,890
wanted her family's money,

108
00:11:52,440 --> 00:11:54,120
and seeing how close she was to her son

109
00:11:54,120 --> 00:11:55,120
made you jealous,

110
00:11:55,320 --> 00:11:56,920
so you wanted to destroy her?

111
00:11:59,150 --> 00:12:00,810
Your imagination is too wild.

112
00:12:03,120 --> 00:12:04,840
And the Ice Queen, Xie Ke.

113
00:12:05,910 --> 00:12:06,960
Did you choose her

114
00:12:08,240 --> 00:12:09,000
to enjoy the thrill

115
00:12:09,000 --> 00:12:11,120
of crushing her under your feet?

116
00:12:13,840 --> 00:12:14,670
Qiao Zishan

117
00:12:15,720 --> 00:12:17,140
had a bright future ahead of her

118
00:12:17,140 --> 00:12:19,000
and she was about to study abroad.

119
00:12:19,240 --> 00:12:20,610
Why did you destroy her?

120
00:12:21,960 --> 00:12:23,620
Was it because her appearance

121
00:12:23,910 --> 00:12:25,710
reminded you of your first love?

122
00:12:29,550 --> 00:12:30,360
Are you done?

123
00:12:33,470 --> 00:12:34,720
Is all this nonsense

124
00:12:35,720 --> 00:12:37,720
something that Officer Li told you?

125
00:12:40,600 --> 00:12:41,150
Yan Ling,

126
00:12:43,100 --> 00:12:44,900
you are a university professor.

127
00:12:45,600 --> 00:12:47,350
At least use your brain.

128
00:12:48,320 --> 00:12:49,720
Just like how you look down
on Li Changning

129
00:12:49,720 --> 00:12:51,180
for being so love-struck.

130
00:12:51,600 --> 00:12:52,600
They are the same,

131
00:12:54,000 --> 00:12:55,060
weak and ignorant.

132
00:12:56,000 --> 00:12:57,720
They chose their own fate.

133
00:12:58,440 --> 00:13:00,100
What does it have to do with me?

134
00:13:01,840 --> 00:13:04,100
Then when I am driven to
a dead end one day,

135
00:13:05,440 --> 00:13:07,440
will you also tell everyone

136
00:13:07,790 --> 00:13:09,390
it was my own choice

137
00:13:09,390 --> 00:13:11,450
and that it has nothing to do with you?

138
00:13:12,030 --> 00:13:13,230
They are just like me.

139
00:13:13,600 --> 00:13:14,630
Out of trust,

140
00:13:16,200 --> 00:13:18,660
we exposed our wounds
and weaknesses to you.

141
00:13:20,030 --> 00:13:20,970
But you

142
00:13:21,960 --> 00:13:23,020
turned all of these

143
00:13:23,270 --> 00:13:25,080
into knives stabbing us.

144
00:13:26,790 --> 00:13:28,950
You keep saying that we are the same,

145
00:13:29,350 --> 00:13:31,080
that we are gifts to each other.

146
00:13:31,840 --> 00:13:33,100
Actually, you chose me

147
00:13:34,360 --> 00:13:36,970
just because I am a wounded prey,

148
00:13:37,120 --> 00:13:39,250
which is easier for you to manipulate—

149
00:13:39,360 --> 00:13:41,020
like a lion picking a gazelle,

150
00:13:42,440 --> 00:13:44,500
always going for the one that's hurt.

151
00:13:45,270 --> 00:13:46,270
Isn't that right?

152
00:13:53,030 --> 00:13:54,830
You really haven't grown at all.

153
00:13:55,790 --> 00:13:57,850
You're still acting like the victim.

154
00:13:58,930 --> 00:14:01,590
You think all the mistakes
were caused by others

155
00:14:02,000 --> 00:14:04,260
and that they have nothing to do with you.

156
00:14:04,510 --> 00:14:05,480
I am not a lion,

157
00:14:06,320 --> 00:14:07,850
and you are not an antelope.

158
00:14:08,240 --> 00:14:09,670
No antelope is like you.

159
00:14:12,600 --> 00:14:13,670
You stole my keys

160
00:14:14,790 --> 00:14:15,870
and entered my room

161
00:14:15,870 --> 00:14:17,200
without my permission,

162
00:14:17,790 --> 00:14:20,120
guarding against your lover like a thief.

163
00:14:21,000 --> 00:14:22,670
Don't pin this on me.

164
00:14:24,240 --> 00:14:25,840
You're just feeling guilty.

165
00:14:26,550 --> 00:14:29,280
If you wanted to destroy
that pen holder so badly,

166
00:14:29,510 --> 00:14:31,390
why didn't you just take it away from home

167
00:14:31,390 --> 00:14:32,390
and throw it away?

168
00:14:35,840 --> 00:14:38,360
You know this is our home.

169
00:14:39,720 --> 00:14:41,710
It's a home for you and me.

170
00:14:43,120 --> 00:14:44,970
It's the warmest

171
00:14:45,150 --> 00:14:46,510
and safest place for me.

172
00:14:47,390 --> 00:14:49,320
Why did you have to ruin it?

173
00:14:50,200 --> 00:14:50,670
Why?

174
00:14:51,960 --> 00:14:53,760
You've really disappointed me.

175
00:14:54,860 --> 00:14:55,990
I used to think that,

176
00:14:56,030 --> 00:14:57,150
in this world,

177
00:14:57,840 --> 00:14:59,370
at least you understood me.

178
00:14:59,720 --> 00:15:00,320
I don't.

179
00:15:02,240 --> 00:15:04,630
I don't understand
where your hatred comes from—

180
00:15:04,630 --> 00:15:06,360
treating all women as enemies,

181
00:15:08,390 --> 00:15:10,440
not even sparing your own sister.

182
00:15:16,040 --> 00:15:16,970
What did you say?

183
00:15:19,440 --> 00:15:21,680
That Wei Zhihua who worked at the salon—

184
00:15:22,590 --> 00:15:24,790
you called her "Edward Scissorhands."

185
00:15:25,360 --> 00:15:26,390
Did you kill her

186
00:15:27,900 --> 00:15:29,500
because her existence

187
00:15:29,630 --> 00:15:31,670
constantly reminded you

188
00:15:32,110 --> 00:15:34,790
of the vile thoughts
you once had about your own sister—

189
00:15:34,790 --> 00:15:36,390
thoughts lower than a beast?

190
00:15:38,420 --> 00:15:39,610
Nonsense!

191
00:15:40,030 --> 00:15:42,990
I didn't. She is my sister.

192
00:15:43,680 --> 00:15:45,150
I never had any of those

193
00:15:45,150 --> 00:15:46,720
disgusting, filthy thoughts about her.

194
00:15:46,720 --> 00:15:47,910
I know you didn't.

195
00:15:48,990 --> 00:15:50,800
But this is your PUA trick

196
00:15:51,630 --> 00:15:54,950
to suppress
and humiliate others, isn't it?

197
00:16:02,900 --> 00:16:05,900
I know you only have family affection
for your sister.

198
00:16:06,630 --> 00:16:07,690
But how does it feel

199
00:16:08,600 --> 00:16:10,680
to be humiliated and misinterpreted?

200
00:16:10,680 --> 00:16:11,520
Does it hurt?

201
00:16:12,870 --> 00:16:15,260
Just like when you knew
I hated Ding Zhibo,

202
00:16:15,560 --> 00:16:16,990
but you said I loved him,

203
00:16:17,160 --> 00:16:19,160
leaving me unable to defend myself.

204
00:16:19,370 --> 00:16:21,880
So you used this set of PUA tricks,

205
00:16:21,920 --> 00:16:23,450
watching the women who love

206
00:16:23,510 --> 00:16:25,850
and trust you crumble in front of you,

207
00:16:26,110 --> 00:16:27,630
thinking you're clever

208
00:16:27,660 --> 00:16:28,560
and smart.

209
00:16:29,260 --> 00:16:30,060
You're wrong.

210
00:16:31,630 --> 00:16:32,960
You being able to hurt us

211
00:16:33,970 --> 00:16:35,500
doesn't mean you're smart.

212
00:16:37,940 --> 00:16:40,000
It's because you have no bottom line.

213
00:16:41,170 --> 00:16:42,360
You have no heart.

214
00:16:43,640 --> 00:16:44,810
I have no heart?

215
00:16:46,480 --> 00:16:48,040
If I didn't care about you,

216
00:16:48,850 --> 00:16:51,280
how could you ever hurt me like this?

217
00:16:56,120 --> 00:16:57,490
I really do love you.

218
00:16:59,730 --> 00:17:01,060
I don't want to lose you.

219
00:17:03,190 --> 00:17:05,859
I don't want you
to leave me like my sister did.

220
00:17:09,940 --> 00:17:11,650
What have you done

221
00:17:13,520 --> 00:17:15,450
for your so-called "not leaving"?

222
00:17:17,800 --> 00:17:18,760
Officer Li

223
00:17:20,050 --> 00:17:23,109
found the old policeman
who handled the case back then.

224
00:17:25,900 --> 00:17:27,900
He said the one who called the police

225
00:17:29,460 --> 00:17:31,790
to report your sister for drug possession

226
00:17:33,590 --> 00:17:35,170
was a kid.

227
00:17:38,590 --> 00:17:39,480
Sister...

228
00:17:39,600 --> 00:17:48,780
[Public phone]

229
00:17:41,350 --> 00:17:44,770
Sister, take me with you.

230
00:17:51,400 --> 00:17:52,550
Study hard.

231
00:17:53,720 --> 00:17:55,050
I will come back for you.

232
00:17:58,180 --> 00:18:03,790
[Public phone]

233
00:18:02,270 --> 00:18:02,960
Sister.

234
00:18:30,510 --> 00:18:31,910
I want to call the police.

235
00:18:31,920 --> 00:18:34,740
Jian, no, Chen Lijian is taking drugs.

236
00:18:35,000 --> 00:18:37,200
He also wants to run away with Xiao Yuan.

237
00:19:10,690 --> 00:19:12,420
-Freeze!
-Police! Freeze!

238
00:19:12,510 --> 00:19:13,100
Get down!

239
00:19:14,350 --> 00:19:15,010
Don't move!

240
00:19:15,030 --> 00:19:16,960
Who told you to grab my instrument?

241
00:19:17,630 --> 00:19:18,230
Get down!

242
00:19:18,480 --> 00:19:19,140
Don't move!

243
00:19:38,240 --> 00:19:38,970
Does it hurt?

244
00:19:41,830 --> 00:19:42,490
No.

245
00:19:47,160 --> 00:19:48,490
Since I've been gone,

246
00:19:50,400 --> 00:19:51,400
you've suffered.

247
00:19:54,110 --> 00:19:54,720
I haven't.

248
00:20:01,200 --> 00:20:02,660
I promise to take you away.

249
00:20:03,200 --> 00:20:05,130
I won't let you get beaten anymore.

250
00:20:07,000 --> 00:20:08,600
Will you really take me away?

251
00:20:14,750 --> 00:20:16,000
Jian has two more years

252
00:20:16,000 --> 00:20:17,670
to serve in Ningxia.

253
00:20:18,310 --> 00:20:20,850
I'm planning to open a hair salon there

254
00:20:20,880 --> 00:20:22,140
called "Yuan's Salon"

255
00:20:22,750 --> 00:20:25,550
so I can earn money
while waiting for him to get out.

256
00:20:25,920 --> 00:20:28,780
Then we can go together to Harbor Island

257
00:20:28,920 --> 00:20:31,490
to watch a concert at Hongkan Stadium.

258
00:20:33,920 --> 00:20:34,380
Sister,

259
00:20:36,110 --> 00:20:37,770
take me with you to make money.

260
00:20:37,920 --> 00:20:39,240
You can't make money.

261
00:20:41,160 --> 00:20:42,300
You must study hard.

262
00:20:42,510 --> 00:20:43,920
You are the smartest in the family.

263
00:20:43,920 --> 00:20:45,420
I am really studying hard.

264
00:20:47,110 --> 00:20:47,710
Really.

265
00:20:48,680 --> 00:20:50,940
I know you've got this kind of potential.

266
00:20:51,310 --> 00:20:52,270
For the rest of my life,

267
00:20:52,270 --> 00:20:54,030
I can only do haircuts for others.

268
00:20:54,030 --> 00:20:55,090
You are different.

269
00:20:55,310 --> 00:20:58,070
You're going to be a PhD, a doctor,

270
00:20:59,720 --> 00:21:00,850
wielding a scalpel.

271
00:21:01,350 --> 00:21:03,880
You've always been
so skillful with your hands.

272
00:21:03,880 --> 00:21:06,080
You're going to the best universities,

273
00:21:06,510 --> 00:21:08,710
maybe Shenchuan, maybe Harbor Island,

274
00:21:09,030 --> 00:21:10,890
and I'll work to pay your tuition.

275
00:21:12,270 --> 00:21:12,810
No.

276
00:21:13,640 --> 00:21:15,110
I just had a dream.

277
00:21:19,070 --> 00:21:19,720
Yuan!

278
00:21:20,270 --> 00:21:20,970
Yuan!

279
00:21:21,160 --> 00:21:21,860
Sister!

280
00:21:22,310 --> 00:21:23,000
Sister!

281
00:21:23,480 --> 00:21:24,550
I'm never coming back

282
00:21:24,550 --> 00:21:26,520
to this house again.

283
00:21:26,750 --> 00:21:29,060
Sister, wait for me!

284
00:21:30,160 --> 00:21:30,880
Sister,

285
00:21:31,270 --> 00:21:32,630
take me with you!

286
00:21:32,720 --> 00:21:33,550
Sister!

287
00:21:35,270 --> 00:21:36,030
