506
00:36:06,930 --> 00:36:09,190
It was attacked by a pod of killer whales.

507
00:36:09,630 --> 00:36:11,820
It struggled for over 4 hours,

508
00:36:12,230 --> 00:36:14,250
and eventually lost its dorsal fin.

509
00:36:16,550 --> 00:36:20,920
The crew said its blood
would attract predators,

510
00:36:21,440 --> 00:36:23,830
the wound would get infected by seawater,

511
00:36:23,880 --> 00:36:25,940
and it definitely wouldn't survive.

512
00:36:29,280 --> 00:36:30,540
Sometimes I feel

513
00:36:31,460 --> 00:36:33,640
like I am that humpback whale.

514
00:36:34,190 --> 00:36:35,630
The wound hasn't healed,

515
00:36:36,840 --> 00:36:39,960
and the smell of blood
attracts new hunters.

