529
00:37:06,960 --> 00:37:08,590
will ever fully heal?

530
00:37:13,300 --> 00:37:14,990
But I am still alive,

531
00:37:17,190 --> 00:37:19,780
which means this wound isn't fatal.

532
00:37:20,880 --> 00:37:25,140
What's truly fatal is surrendering to it.

533
00:37:26,280 --> 00:37:28,940
Just like the story
I haven't finished telling.

534
00:37:29,760 --> 00:37:30,760
Five years later,

535
00:37:31,230 --> 00:37:34,400
