545
00:38:08,350 --> 00:38:09,410
in your own hearts,

546
00:38:10,110 --> 00:38:11,850
just like I do.

547
00:38:13,030 --> 00:38:14,640
But the fact

548
00:38:15,610 --> 00:38:17,010
that we are here together

549
00:38:17,150 --> 00:38:18,960
shows that we no longer see

550
00:38:20,960 --> 00:38:23,030
those wounds as a shame to hide.

551
00:38:24,030 --> 00:38:25,180
It shows that we are

552
00:38:26,030 --> 00:38:27,470
